   :feedback_a: Yes, three bits will enable you to represent eight different values
   :feedback_b: No, four bits is more than you need
   :feedback_c: No, two bits can only represent four different values
   :feedback_d: No, five bits is more than you need

   Imagine that you want to create a code to represent ethnicity; the choices are African-American,
   Caucasian, Hispanic, Other, Prefer not to say. How many bits will you need?